org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.stellaris

Class FlashLoaderManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.stellaris.FlashLoaderManager

  • public class FlashLoaderManager
extends java.lang.Object
    FlashLoaderManager manages the process of writing a new firmware image. to a Stellaris flash loader. The target system must be put into firmware update mode by external means before using the functionality herein.
